      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 30 secs</p>",
