      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>roasted garlic paste</strong>, <strong>tomato paste </strong>and<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 30 secs further</p><p>Add your <strong>Chinese rice wine </strong>with a generous pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min further</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
