    {
      "instruction": "<p>Set the <strong>tomato gnocchi </strong>in the centre of the table, ready to share</p><p>Crumble your<strong> goats' cheese</strong> all over the gnocchi and top with your <strong>salad</strong></p><p>Drizzle with some<strong> olive oil</strong>, season with a grind of<strong> pepper </strong>and let everyone dig in</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
